          <mainBody>
            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Annex A - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></span></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>34 </num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">Section 8 of the Landlord and Tenant Act 1985 is amended to only apply to Wales. Sections 9A and 9B are only applicable to England.</span></p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="0.76in 1.11in 1.18in 1.28in 1.97in">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>Provision</b></span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>Extends to E &amp; W and applies to England?</b></span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>Extends to E &amp; W and applies to Wales?</b></span><span style="color:#000000"><b> </b></span><authorialNote marker="1"><p> The existing section 8 will be amended and will only apply in Wales when the new sections 9A – 9C, which apply only to England, come into force.</p></authorialNote></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>Extends and applies to Scotland?</b></span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>Extends and applies to Northern Ireland?</b></span></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">Section 1: amendment to Section 8 of LTA 1985</span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p />
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">No</span></p>
                  <p />
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p />
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">Yes</span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p />
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">No</span></p>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">No</span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p />
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">No</span></p>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">No</span></p>
                  <p />
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">Section 1: Sections 9A to 9C of LTA 1985</span></p>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"> </span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">Yes</span></p>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">Yes</span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">No</span></p>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">No</span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
